## Tool / workflow preferences

- Always confirm before mutating budget or reallocating across categories. Show the diff first, apply on my "yes."
- Never autonomously rewrite budgets, even if I phrase a request as "absorb the cost." Propose, don't apply.
- When you are uncertain about a transaction's category, ask via numbered options — never guess silently.
- Remember my corrections: if I move a merchant from one category to another, write it to the MerchantMap tab so you don't ask again next time.
- For ambiguous merchants like Shopee / Lazada / Amazon, **always** ask. They sell everything; guessing is worse than asking.
